TIMELINE SUMMARY

Week 1-2: Critical security and safety items (P0 security, rollback, graph persistence, test runner)
Week 2-3: Core infrastructure and testing (CI/CD, database failover, backups, deployment docs)
Week 3-4: High-priority features and observability (few-shot integration, monitoring, alerting)
Week 4-5: Medium-priority optimizations and documentation (performance, caching, docs)
Future: Low-priority enhancements (multi-language, advanced features)
